      "text": "莉央さんはお店のお手伝いはしていたんですか？",
      "startTime": 213.0006277087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02-rio025.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんよ。店が忙しい時は、私もエプロンをつけて\n注文を取りに行ったりしたわ",
      "startTime": 220.8672898534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02-rio026.m4a",
      "text": "料理が好きになったのも\nきっと両親の手伝いがきっかけね",
      "startTime": 225.0672806981,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "お話を聞いていると、歌やダンスの話は全然\n出てきませんが、芸能界に興味を持ったきっかけは？",
      "startTime": 231.1519141864,
