      "text": "歌は好きだったわ。でも、まさか\n自分がステージに立とうなんて、思ってもいなかったわ",
      "startTime": 238.9154182675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02-rio028.m4a",
      "text": "私は高校を卒業したら\n両親とお店をやっていくつもりだったもの",
      "startTime": 245.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
