      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02-rio029.m4a",
      "text": "でも、父が突然亡くなって\n店の経営が危なくなって……",
      "startTime": 251.7820910377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02-rio030.m4a",
      "text": "我が家は、店を手放す寸前まで追い詰められたの\n私、それだけはどうしても嫌だった。だから――",
      "startTime": 258.8554529192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02-rio031.m4a",
      "text": "母を経済的に支えて店を守るために、私は上京して\nアイドルになる決心をしたのよ",
      "startTime": 269.215436578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "まだ若いのに、そこまでの決心をするのは\n相当なことですよね",
      "startTime": 274.9666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02-rio032.m4a",
      "text": "幼い私が大金を稼ぐ方法は他になかったのよ\n……ごめんね、全然キラキラした理由じゃなくて",
      "startTime": 281.9679309449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことはありません。莉央さんらしいです\n腹が据わっていて、凄いと思いますよ",
      "startTime": 288.8027499485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02-rio033.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、ありがとう。それからは、知っての通り\n私は葵と出会って、そしてデビューしたの",
      "startTime": 297.0259130401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_02-rio034.m4a",
      "text": "順調だったわ。このまま成功出来ると思ってた\n……でもある時、大きな壁にぶつかったのよ",
      "startTime": 306.2592606149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
